text: Stanisław Jasiński (born 13 November 1959) is a Polish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Poland Category:Equestrians at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Masovian Voivodeship
